# Build output and run-time state. Seeds, the dictionary, the README, the
# manifests, and the committed Cargo.lock are tracked; everything below is
# machine-generated and gitignored — which also keeps it invisible to
# `just scan-self` (the CLI honours .gitignore), so an evolved corpus or a
# crash reproducer can never trip the dogfood scan.
target/
corpus/
artifacts/
coverage/
